OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FRare works from a number of
OL,8,Fcontemporary artists including Sir
OL,9,FGrayson Perry, Es Devlin and Nan
OL,10,FGoldin will go up for auction to raise
OL,11,Fmoney for Palestine.
OL,13,FThe auction and public exhibition,
OL,14,Falso featuring works from artists
OL,15,FCharlie Mackesy, Brian Eno and Sarah
OL,16,FBall, will take place later this month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
