FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FOrganised by Choose Love, Gideon
OL,8,FBerger Studio, Hope 93 Gallery and art
OL,9,Fdealer Zayna Al-Saleh, all profits
OL,10,Fraised will go towards the Together
OL,11,FFor Palestine Fund, held by Choose
OL,12,FLove, to support Palestinian-led
OL,13,Forganisations.
OL,15,FAmong the pieces going under the
OL,16,Fhammer is Devlin's Redraw The Edges Of
OL,17,FYourself, Sir Grayson's ceramics work
OL,18,FLady With Fireworks, based on a
OL,19,Fminiature in the Wallace Collection,
OL,20,Fand Goldin's Holy Sheep, Rathmullan,
OL,21,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FThe auction will also see Jeremy
OL,8,FDeller's new work with Ed Hall, The
OL,9,FConstant Buzz Of A Drone, go under the
OL,10,Fhammer among many other collectables
OL,11,Fincluding two works by Khaled Hourani,
OL,12,FWatermelon Flag and Kendaka, Nabil
OL,13,FAnani's Nabulus and Misan Harriman's
OL,14,FBrothers In Protest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
