FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FJosie Fernandez-Marelli, chief
OL,8,Fexecutive of Choose Love, said: "In
OL,9,Fthese turbulent and frightening times,
OL,10,Fit's more important than ever that we
OL,11,Fput humanity first, and make sure
OL,12,Ffamilies and children have what they
OL,13,Fneed to survive.
OL,15,F"There is still an urgent need to
OL,16,Fsupport vital organisations providing
OL,17,Fhumanitarian aid on the ground in Gaza.
OL,26,@pD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
