FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,F"We are proud to stand with Together
OL,8,FFor Palestine, and deeply grateful to
OL,9,Fevery artist for their contributions,
OL,10,Fsupporting our partners to save as
OL,11,Fmany lives as possible."
OL,13,FThe auction follows on from the
OL,14,FTogether For Palestine concert, which
OL,15,Fraised more than #2 million for
OL,16,Fhumanitarian organisations.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
