FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FThe profits will go towards supporting
OL,8,Femergency relief efforts in Palestine
OL,9,Fincluding food and water, healthcare,
OL,10,Fshelter, mental health support and the
OL,11,Flargest orphan care programme in Gaza.
OL,13,FPalestinian painter Malak Mattar
OL,14,Fadded: "Since working on the Together
OL,15,FFor Palestine concert with incredible
OL,16,Fartists like Es Devlin and Brian Eno
OL,17,Fand witnessing the moving public
OL,18,Freception and response to visual art,
OL,19,FI realised the true power of artists
OL,20,Fstanding together for humanity and a
OL,21,Fshared cause.
OL,26,@vD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
