PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772640682
OL,3,CArt by Grayson Perry and Es Devlin
OL,4,Camong works going up for Palestine
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,F"This auction is a reflection of that
OL,8,Fsame solidarity, with the aim of
OL,9,Fraising as much as possible for the
OL,10,Fsupported charities."
OL,12,FThe auction will be open for bids from
OL,13,FMarch 26 ` April 9 and an exhibition
OL,14,Fof the works will be open to the
OL,15,Fpublic at Hope 93 Gallery in London
OL,16,Fover the same period.
